name: Anna Prom Night Salon: Girls Makeup, Dressup Games
name_original: Anna Prom Night Salon: Girls Makeup, Dressup Games
description:
Princess Anna is very excited, is going to graduate and there will be a great party at night. The castle will be full of many guests, so she must be very cute for the end-of-class party.

Anna and her friends are popular in her high school, she must be the cutest one for being the leader of the group.

Let's dress Anna with the latest fashion for princesses. Choose nice dresses or pants, some heels, and many other accessories, that every girl should use. She's going to be the prom queen.
There is a great variety of suits to combine as you like.

- many princesses crown
- A lot of dresses
- many tops
- many hairstyles, pants, skirts, heels and more

Do you want to be a fashion designer?
Use your creativity to put together the best combinations.

Be a fashion designer and have fun with our dress up games for girls.

Dress up games for girls.
